These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, social-worker
1. the paramedic is in an even position##4
2. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | reading | drawing |
| Job     | social-worker    | paramedic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, parkour
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | tea | milk        |
| Sport      | swimming  | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, salsa
There are 2 different nationalities: british, american
1. the british is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | punk |
| Nationality   | british | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, water
There 2 different types of food: tomato, grapefruit
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | sprite      | water |
| Food       | tomato | grapefruit    |

 #################################

 
