.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, skiing
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, bike
1. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | skiing | basketball  |
| Transport   | bike  | van |

